    "title": "Supply Chain Manager - AFL Logistics - Freshers Welcome",
    "description": "Join the AFL Logistics family as a Supply Chain Manager in Ranchi. We believe in empowering our employees with the tools, training, and environment they need to succeed.\n\nAbout AFL Logistics:\nAFL Logistics is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage a fleet of vehicles and coordinate with drivers\n• Manage relationships with third-party logistics providers\n• Optimize delivery routes to reduce cost and improve efficiency\n• Manage reverse logistics and return merchandise authorization\n• Coordinate with customer service teams to resolve delivery issues\n• Oversee end-to-end logistics operations for timely delivery\n• Handle customs clearance for import and export shipments\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBA from a recognized university\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Route Optimization\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain Management\n• Proficiency in Cold Chain Logistics\n• Proficiency in KPI Monitoring\n• Proficiency in ERP Systems\n• Proficiency in INCOTERMS\n• Proficiency in Vendor Management\n• Proficiency in TMS\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Professional development and training programs\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Ranchi, Jharkhand, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with AFL Logistics!",
